{"type": "article", "id": 16747, "title": "柯布西耶纪念小件", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-29T07:20:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004252qFmQjpEXNVuA9YRf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些木制的小物件是为了纪念柯布西耶逝世 50 周年，材料来自一颗种植在莱芒湖畔小别墅（villa “le lac”）庭院露台的泡桐树，因为无法治愈而送到了木工厂。意大利家具品牌卡西纳邀请设计师 Jaime Hayon 创作这组物品，包括鸟居、小鸟和秋千，它们可以用来存放明信片和书本，简单而富有诗意。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144031dGkaV6DzNAm4YO0U.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"563\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144032RVOCkQWwjhL39imE.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"563\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144032V4FiI8Z1dnStghDk.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"563\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144034nFbvCkTweKZJtcr7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}